c/sets/72057594053063859/ January 2006 images of Trotsky House, Mexico City]\n* [http://www.marxist.com/LeninAndTrotsky/ Lenin and Trotsky\u2014 What they Really Stood For] by [[Alan Woods (politician)|Alan Woods]] and [[Ted Grant]]\n* [http://libcom.org/library/contradiction-trotsky-claude-lefort ''The Contradiction of Trotsky''] by [[Claude Lefort]]\n* [http://www.marxists.org/archive/trotsky/index.htm The Leon Trotsky Internet Archive] at [[Marxists.org]] (under [[GFDL|GNU Free Documentation License]])\n* [http://fora.tv/2009/07/28/Uncommon_Knowledge_Christopher_Hitchens__Robert_Service] ''Uncommon Knowledge'' Interview with [[Christopher Hitchens]] and [[Robert Service (historian)|Robert Service]] on Leon Trotsky\n* [http://jewishhistorylectures.org/2012/04/26/leon-trotsky-jews-on-the-left/ Leon Trotsky: Jews on the Left, Video Lecture by Dr. [[Henry Abramson]]]\n* [http://hdl.handle.net/10622/ARCH01483 Lev Davidovi\u010d Trockij / International Left Opposition Archives] at the [[International Institute of Social History]]\n* {{PM20|FID=pe/017601}}\n* [https://libcom.org/library/the-bolsheviks-and-workers-control-solidarity-group] An historical presentation of the party state that replaced the soviets.\n\n===Works===\n*{{marxists.org|trotsky|Leon Trotsky}}\n* {{Gutenberg author |id=Trotsky,+Leon | name=Leon Trotsky}}\n* {{FadedPage|id=Trotsky, Leon|name=Leon Trotsky|author=yes}}\n* {{Internet Archive author |sname=Leon Trotsky}}\n* {{Librivox author |id=4200}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Mikhail Tereshchenko]]<br />(Minister of Foreign Affairs)}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Foreign Minister of Russia|People's Commissar for Foreign Affairs]]|years=1917\u20131918}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Georgy Chicherin]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Nikolai Podvoisky]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of Defence of Soviet Union|People's Commissar for Army and Navy Affairs]]|years=1918\u20131925}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Mikhail Frunze]]}}\n{{S-ach}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Winston Churchill]]}}\n{{S-ttl|ti