rk|Seehausen]].\n\n[[Category:Villages in Saxony-Anhalt]]\n[[Category:Province of Saxony]]\n\n{{Stendal-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geestgottberg"}
